Name: "Red Hat Enterprise Linux SEoL (8.8.x, 8.9.x)"
Description:
"'According to its version, Red Hat Enterprise Linux is 8.8.x or 8.9.x. It is, therefore, no longer maintained by its vendor or provider.
Lack of support implies that no new security patches for the product will be released by the vendor. As a result, it may contain security vulnerabilities.

OS : Red Hat Enterprise Linux 8.8 (Ootpa)
Security End of Life : May 31, 2025

Port: 0
Protocol: TCP
